St. Christopher medallion

797
01:11:57,835 --> 01:11:58,836
touched him.

798
01:11:59,663 --> 01:12:01,142
Whoa.

799
01:12:01,317 --> 01:12:03,014
There’s a story
from a long time ago.

800
01:12:04,798 --> 01:12:06,409
There was this trucker
who got away.

801
01:12:06,583 --> 01:12:10,195
